Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:10.40,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Juntando nossos sonhos e esperanças,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.03,0:01:16.69,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,em busca dos nossos desejos...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:19.54,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uma moeda no bolso!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:22.29,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,E você quer ser meu Amigo?
