Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:39.71,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Vamos pôr um fim na noite monótona!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:45.32,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Não temos interesse em baús de tesouro
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.38,0:01:48.46,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Um romance no bolso!
